<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Spring AI - Structured Output Examples</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" th:href="@{/css/home.css}">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <h1>🤖 Spring AI - Structured Output Examples</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">BeanOutputConverter, MapOutputConverter, ListOutputConverter 샘플</p>
        </header>
        
        <div class="converter-selector">
            <label for="converterType">출력 변환기 선택:</label>
            <select id="converterType">
                <option value="bean">🎬 Bean Output - Single Actor Films</option>
                <option value="list-bean">🎬 Bean Output - Multiple Actors Films</option>
                <option value="map">🗺️ Map Output - Structured Data</option>
                <option value="list">📝 List Output - Simple List</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Bean Output (Single) -->
        <div id="bean-section" class="input-section">
            <h3>🎬 BeanOutputConverter - Single Actor</h3>
            <p class="description">특정 배우의 영화 목록을 ActorsFilms Bean 객체로 반환합니다.</p>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="beanActor">배우 이름:</label>
                <input type="text" id="beanActor" placeholder="예: Tom Hanks" value="Tom Hanks">
                <button onclick="callBeanOutput()">조회하기</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Bean Output (List) -->
        <div id="list-bean-section" class="input-section" style="display:none;">
            <h3>🎬 BeanOutputConverter - Multiple Actors</h3>
            <p class="description">여러 배우의 영화 목록을 List&lt;ActorsFilms&gt;로 반환합니다.</p>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="listBeanActors">배우 이름들:</label>
                <input type="text" id="listBeanActors" placeholder="예: Tom Hanks and Bill Murray" value="Tom Hanks and Bill Murray">
                <button onclick="callListBeanOutput()">조회하기</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Map Output -->
        <div id="map-section" class="input-section" style="display:none;">
            <h3>🗺️ MapOutputConverter</h3>
            <p class="description">요청한 정보를 Map&lt;String, Object&gt; 형태로 반환합니다.</p>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="mapSubject">요청 내용:</label>
                <input type="text" id="mapSubject" placeholder="예: an array of numbers from 1 to 9 under they key name 'numbers'" value="an array of numbers from 1 to 9 under they key name 'numbers'">
                <button onclick="callMapOutput()">조회하기</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- List Output -->
        <div id="list-section" class="input-section" style="display:none;">
            <h3>📝 ListOutputConverter</h3>
            <p class="description">주제에 대한 항목들을 List&lt;String&gt; 형태로 반환합니다.</p>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="listSubject">주제:</label>
                <input type="text" id="listSubject" placeholder="예: ice cream flavors" value="ice cream flavors">
                <button onclick="callListOutput()">조회하기</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Loading Indicator -->
        <div id="loading" class="loading" style="display:none;">
            <div class="spinner"></div>
            <p>처리 중...</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Result Section -->
        <div id="result-section" class="result-section" style="display:none;">
            <h3>📊 결과</h3>
            <div id="result-content" class="result-content"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script th:src="@{/js/home.js}"></script>
</body>
</html>
